docs.description: The number of homes per 10,000 that were foreclosed in a given month. docs.name: Zillow Rent Index (Zip Codes): Rentals ZRI Per Sq. Ft. (All Homes) - 19526,Hamburg,PA
docs.description: The Zillow Home Rental Index is Zillow's estimate of the median rental price of all homes within the zip code of 19526, Hamburg, PA. This is derived by taking the estimated rent price for each home and dividing it by the homes square footage. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
